        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "75a37c72-0fdd-4646-bf2a-789995138aef",
        "text": "Government deficit spending is a central point of controversy in economics, with prominent economists holding differing views. - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deficit_spending#Controversy wikipedia]"
      },
      "after": "4ce10e70-62de-4575-9d1e-2f93d83eba84",
      "id": "75a37c72-0fdd-4646-bf2a-789995138aef",
      "date": 1497019072040
